However, all the previous CFJs directly challenged the legality of Indulgence
POs and all were resolved in favor of the legality of Indulgence POs.

>> So I am forced to apply judicial reasoning even to determine whether any POs
>> are in dispute.  There seems to be precedent which would allow me to dismiss
>> this claim out of hand for just this reason.

>I don't see why. A PO is disputed when there is a CFJ "challenging its
